trans-unit.source: The application is unable to connect to the SIL Locale Data Repository to retrieve the latest information about this language. If you create this writing system, the default settings might be incorrect or out of date. Are you sure you want to create a new writing system?
trans-unit.target: Nti' nok tmujb'a'n tib' aq'unb'il xk'utz'ib' ti'j t-xmilal tk'ub'il yol te SIL tu'n ttzaj tq'o'n ak'aj tpokb'al ti'j yolb'il lu'. Qa ma kub' tb'inchana tu'mel tz'ib'b'il lu', jaku mlayx kb'antel tu'n tlaj a txolb'al aq'untl nya b'a'n mo ojtxi o kub' b'inchet. ¿Tajxixya tu'n tkub' tb'inchana jun ak'aj tu'mel tz'ib'b'il?

alt-trans.target: Nti' nok tq'on tib' b'inchab'il ti'j txwilal tkub'il yol te SILtu'n tzaj tq'o'n pokb'al ma yin n-netz tib'aj yolb'il lu'. Qa ma kub' tb'inchana tu'mel tz'ib'il lu', nalyx kb'antel tu'n tlaj a meltz'ul aq'untl nya b'a'n mo ojtxa o kub' b'inchet. ¿Tajxixya tu'n tkub' tb'inchana jun ak'aj tumel tz'ib'il?
